snippet: The Black Knights ended a 13-game losing streak in military service academy games as quarterback Trent Steelman ran for two touchdowns against Air Force.
abstract: Army defeats Air Force, 41-21, in college football.
lead_paragraph: The Black Knights ended a 13-game losing streak in military service academy games as quarterback Trent Steelman ran for two touchdowns against Air Force.
